Package: librockchip-mpp-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: librockchip-mpp6 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Rockchip Media Process Platform (development files)
 This package contains the development headers and libraries
 for the Rockchip Media Process Platform (MPP).
 .
 MPP is the Media Process Platform for Rockchip chips, providing
 unified interfaces for video encoding, decoding, and processing.

Package: librockchip-mpp6
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Description: Rockchip Media Process Platform (shared library)
 This package contains the shared libraries for the Rockchip
 Media Process Platform (MPP).
 .
 MPP provides video codec support including H.264, H.265, VP8,
 VP9, JPEG, and other formats for Rockchip SoCs.

