Description: Rockchip VPU compatibility library
 This package provides a compatibility library for the legacy
 Rockchip VPU API, built on top of the new MPP framework.

Package: rockchip-mpp-demos
Architecture: any
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Depends: librockchip-mpp6 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Rockchip Media Process Platform demo programs
 This package contains demo and test programs for the Rockchip
 Media Process Platform (MPP).
 .
 Examples include video encoding/decoding demos and test utilities.
